Packaged by Neha Sharma <neha@fnal.gov>

The upstream source tarball for Bestman is created by the following procedure:

  REPO=https://github.com/opensciencegrid/bestman2
  VER=2.3.0c  # set appropriately

  git clone $REPO
  cd bestman2
  git archive --prefix=bestman2-$VER/ --format=tgz v$VER > bestman2-$VER.tar.gz

OR one of:

  wget --content-disposition $REPO/archive/v$VER.tar.gz

  curl -JLO $REPO/archive/v$VER.tar.gz

The tarball that contains the dependencies can be downloaded from
http://vdt.cs.wisc.edu/upstream/bestman2/2.3.0/dependent.jars.tar.gz
